      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u sure about the pseudoephedrine though? i read online somewhere that it might cause issues with blood flow to the placenta. if it's \"considered safe\" for most people, does that mean it's actually okay for me specifically right now? i'm just really desperate for some relief because i can't breathe through my nose at all.",
